        "label": "Map-Reduce with Send",
        "text": "Chunker produces a list of chunks. The Map node fans one parallel branch per chunk (LangGraph Send). Each branch summarizes its chunk, the Join concatenates summaries, and Reducer writes the final overview."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "start-1",
      "type": "start",
      "position": { "x": 40, "y": 260 },
      "data": { "label": "Start", "inputVariables": ["document"] }
